Sentencas: Layered perovskite oxides, Y1-xBixBaCo2O5+delta (YBBCx, x = 0.0-0.2) were investigated as cathodes for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Effects of Bi-doping on structure and properties of YBaCo2O5+δ layered perovskite cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: XRD results indicate the YBBCx could be indexed to a tetragonal phase with trace of 3 x 3 x 1 superstructure configuration.
Titulo: Effects of Bi-doping on structure and properties of YBaCo2O5+δ layered perovskite cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: No significant change in thermal expansion coefficients (TECs) was detected with the Bi-doping, and the TECs were 15.7-16.8 x 10(-6) K-1 at 100-935 degrees C in air.
Titulo: Effects of Bi-doping on structure and properties of YBaCo2O5+δ layered perovskite cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Although the Bi-doping results in a decrease in conductivity of the YBBCx, the x = 0.2 sample still shows higher conductivity than that of a standard SOFC cathode (similar to 100 S cm(-1)).
Titulo: Effects of Bi-doping on structure and properties of YBaCo2O5+δ layered perovskite cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Additionally, the Bi-doping leads to an enhancement in the electrochemical performance mainly due to improved ion and electron charge transfers.
Titulo: Effects of Bi-doping on structure and properties of YBaCo2O5+δ layered perovskite cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Among the YBBCx compositions, the YBBC0.2 cathode shows the lowest polarization resistance (R-p) of 0.034 Omega cm(2) at 700.
Titulo: Effects of Bi-doping on structure and properties of YBaCo2O5+δ layered perovskite cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: For a single cell with 300 mu m thick La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O3-delta (LSGM) and YBBC0.2 cathode, a peak power density (P-max) of 537 mW cm(-2) at 700 degrees C was achieved with no significant deterioration in performance after a 100-h testing.
Titulo: Effects of Bi-doping on structure and properties of YBaCo2O5+δ layered perovskite cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
